usage: extract_detector_report_scope.py [-h] [--source SOURCE]
                                        [--format {json}] [--output OUTPUT]
                                        report

Extract static detector-report annotations as style-editing scope hints.

positional arguments:
  report           Local HTML detector report

options:
  -h, --help       show this help message and exit
  --source SOURCE  Optional source document used for unique exact normalized
                   mapping
  --format {json}  Output format (currently only json)
  --output OUTPUT  Optional path for the JSON result
